---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Experience">
	<section>
		<h1>Experience</h1>
		<div class="git-log">
			<div class="ascii-header">commit history (HEAD -> main)</div>
			<div class="log-entry">
				<span class="marker">*</span> <span class="commit-hash">2025-12-15</span> (<span class="branch">HEAD -> main</span>) - <span class="title">Backend & Ai Developer</span> at <span class="company">Licichat</span> (<span class="date">2023-01 - Present</span>)
			</div>
			<div class="log-body">
        Develop a RAG based system for a chatbot llm, specilized in peruvian tenders for for a tutor and guide in the application process.
        I've used backend frameworks and cloud services:
        - Google Cloud - Cloud Run
        - Supabase
        - FastAPI
			</div>
			<div class="separator">|</div>
			<div class="log-entry">
				<span class="marker">*</span> <span class="commit-hash">2025-070-12</span> - <span class="title">Software Engineer</span> at <span class="company">InnovateLabs</span> (<span class="date">2021-06 - 2022-12</span>)
			</div>
			<div class="log-body">
				Developed full-stack web applications, collaborated on agile teams, mentored junior developers. Stack: React, Python, PostgreSQL.
			</div>
			<div class="separator">| \</div>
			<div class="log-entry">
				<span class="marker">|</span> <span class="commit-hash">branch-off</span> - <span class="title">Project Lead</span> at <span class="company">InnovateLabs</span> (<span class="date">2022-03 - 2022-06</span>)
			</div>
			<div class="log-body">
				Managed a team of 5 developers on a critical project, delivered ahead of schedule. Tools: Jira, Git, CI/CD pipelines.
			</div>
			<div class="separator">| /</div>
			<div class="log-entry">
				<span class="marker">*</span> <span class="commit-hash">ghi9012</span> - <span class="title">Junior Developer</span> at <span class="company">StartupXYZ</span> (<span class="date">2019-08 - 2021-05</span>)
			</div>
			<div class="log-body">
				Built responsive websites, learned modern JS frameworks, contributed to open-source projects. Languages: JavaScript, HTML/CSS.
			</div>
			<div class="separator">|</div>
			<div class="log-entry">
				<span class="marker">*</span> <span class="commit-hash">jkl3456</span> - <span class="title">Intern</span> at <span class="company">CodeMasters</span> (<span class="date">2018-06 - 2018-08</span>)
			</div>
			<div class="log-body">
				Assisted in debugging and testing, gained experience in version control and code reviews. First exposure to professional development.
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<style>
		.git-log {
			font-family: 'Iosevka', monospace;
			font-size: 1rem;
			line-height: 1.5;
			color: var(--fg);
			white-space: pre-wrap;
			word-wrap: break-word;
			max-width: 90vw;
			margin: 0;
			position: sticky;
		}

		.ascii-header {
			color: var(--cyan);
			font-weight: bold;
		}

		.marker {
			color: var(--yellow);
			font-weight: bold;
		}

		.commit-hash {
			color: var(--green);
		}

		.branch {
			color: var(--red);
		}

		.title {
			color: var(--yellow);
		}

		.company {
			color: var(--blue);
		}

		.date {
			color: var(--fg-dim);
		}

		.log-body {
			margin-left: 2rem;
			color: var(--fg);
		}

		.separator {
			color: var(--fg);
			font-weight: bold;
		}
	</style>
</BaseLayout>
